The '''CardSafe''' was one of the most talked-about and well known [[Restaurant/Legends|restaurants]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], during the early [[Standard year/Legends|years]] of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. Established by [[Ortolan/Legends|Ortolan]] [[Chef/Legends|chef]] [[Handree Braman]], the CardSafe was known for its use of local wildlife in the main dishes, including [[Hawk-bat/Legends|hawk-bats]].

